    .about-me
      p ORows empowers teams to manage their data with an Excel (spreadsheet) like interface.
      p Most great things are usually built by an organized team of people working on a common goal. At the heart, what ORows offers is simplicity, order and collaboration.
      P Easily define your data schema and set complex nested relationships using the intuitive visual editor.
      P Add fields such as images, files, rich text, multiselect e.t.c.
      P Granular permissions not only at row level but field level too. You can share parts of data with others for editing or have it view-only with ability for commenting and accepting suggestions.
      P Set validations, calculated fields, and custom formatting.
      P Create views to filter, sort, group and transform your data to share it as a chart or report.
      P Version history is automatically saved. If you make a mistake, or someone accidentally adds bad data, you can always audit and fix it.
      P Import/export from excel, csv, json or simply just copy-paste. You could even expose views as a REST API and receive callbacks when something changes.
      P Building a serverless website or app with ORows as your database and management portal is easy peasy. Get from idea to execution within minutes.
      p Your team can work offline and automatically sync when they're connected. Your data is always with you.
      p Send an email to hello@orows.com if you are interested.
